{"tid":2430080,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新加坡：支持民族自決 反對政府以武力對付平民 緬甸不應阻止國際介入","createTime":"2021-03-02T16:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T20:21:48.000Z","uid":362199,"like":6,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ca282d4be7f1d2fe23ab4e98dcf341544d8736","tid":2430080,"uid":362199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T16:43:09.000Z","msg":"東南亞國家協會（ASEAN）今天舉行非正式部長級會議，討論緬甸情勢。據星國外交部公布資料，維文（Vivian Balakrishnan）於會中表示，新加坡對緬甸安全部隊向示威者使用致命武器感到「震驚」；在任何情況下，對手無寸鐵的人民使用致命武器都是「無任何藉口可言」的行為。<br />\n<br />\n維文表示，當務之急是避免情勢快速惡化，新加坡呼籲緬甸軍方公開承諾克制，不再使用致命武器，並確保不會有進一步的暴力及流血事件。<br />\n<br />\n他說，數以百萬計、走上街頭抗議的民眾有決心要讓緬甸回到民主治理。新加坡一向秉持的原則是緬甸未來應由緬甸人民決定。<br />\n<br />\n另外，維文表示，他在參加會議前與聯合國秘書長古特瑞斯（Antonio Guterres）緬甸事務特使柏其納（Christine Schraner Burgener）通話。新加坡強烈支持柏其納訪問緬甸，且呼籲緬甸軍方盡快協助安排這項訪問，讓她可與翁山蘇姬、緬甸總統溫敏（Win Myint）等相關各方會面。<br />\n<br />\n維文也說，希望在這個關鍵時刻，緬甸不要試圖防止東協與外部夥伴互動。美國拜登政府已多次表達與東協往來的意願；約2個月前，東協外長們也表達與美國往來的興趣，因此，新加坡強烈持支持東協-美國外長會議的提議，並認為會議應盡快舉行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/5290152?zarsrc=30&amp;utm_source=zalo&amp;utm_medium=zalo&amp;utm_campaign=zalo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5599%2F5290152%3Fzarsrc%3D30%26utm_source%3Dzalo%26utm_medium%3Dzalo%26utm_campaign%3Dzalo&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiukXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=f4e31fa8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/5290152?zarsrc=30&amp;utm_source=zalo&amp;utm_medium=zalo&amp;utm_campaign=zalo</a>"},{"pid":"5c2d0fd7c97417c7b2b469bd639ac286d07da689","tid":2430080,"uid":362199,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T16:43:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.roc-taiwan.org/mm/post/7196.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.roc-taiwan.org%2Fmm%2Fpost%2F7196.html&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiukXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=42a30825\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.roc-taiwan.org/mm/post/7196.html</a><br />\n<br />\n新加坡佔緬甸第一季FDI第一位"},{"pid":"45ac252ae2b63270bc720004e1cb9a78c0ad2178","tid":2430080,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T16:45:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da057834e741fc692bfb05dcd73a5a5f294ffc02","tid":2430080,"uid":182210,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T16:47:40.000Z","msg":"新加坡同日本嘅投資凍過水 俾中國過咗一棟"},{"pid":"c53ab97fbcc2e05dafcbfad55434b36366885820","tid":2430080,"uid":66324,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T16:48:56.000Z","msg":"但又反對制裁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08feec66b93d97aa15f1e0b2f16820f028873051","tid":2430080,"uid":225798,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T16:49:07.000Z","msg":"你班撚屌前兩日先同中國軍演"},{"pid":"6e711d19b7e14b4890ceea1eee677cf90370f5cd","tid":2430080,"uid":35430,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T17:07:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死波狗馬嬲<br />\n上兩年唔係咁講"},{"pid":"3e4967c1a08660c28ba1428347d2a3807ba21c6b","tid":2430080,"uid":2110,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T17:20:51.000Z","msg":"睇地圖，如果中國收服左緬甸，佢地就可以直接跳過馬六甲海峽直出印度洋，馬嬲坡對中國黎講就唔再咁重要"},{"pid":"776a523d931110417e4b75ea36aed4140182a813","tid":2430080,"uid":266342,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T17:44:37.000Z","msg":"新加坡呢班仆街<br />\n到底你隻屎眼睇唔睇到<br />\n其實從頭到尾都係支那作怪<br />\n<br />\n成日話自己個根喺嗰度<br />\n唔好意思福建同廣東係被支那已經一早侵略左<br />\n根本就唔肯認清現實"},{"pid":"45338082024592bc3c4180d1ba83dca7fdd4ddc4","tid":2430080,"uid":3659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T17:45:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾馬騮，冇國魂，冇民族內涵<br />\n憑咩存在<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79bdc1b376c4bb53407e898cfad8382a44cb3f0f","tid":2430080,"uid":38164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T19:21:46.000Z","msg":"坡狗<br />\n...."},{"pid":"fd004caea5ef82d978bc5647d3782b3ca43a715c","tid":2430080,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T19:26:43.000Z","msg":"屌....呢D 下九流地方軍頭弱雞到，而家現代人比教學教到帝國主義好撚邪惡，根本呢D 仆街軍頭就需要文明國度既軍隊出兵打撚柒佢，重建秩序。比左半個世紀以上比呢堆低等文化生物自己管自己，結果多年黎都係一篤屎，仲要近埋支那呢個世紀大魔頭度反攻自由世界"},{"pid":"48982308d9bc08da1aaf95deefeb0c235d91053b","tid":2430080,"uid":40216,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T19:34:52.000Z","msg":"新加坡就真係企自己利益講野<br />\n香港人學下"},{"pid":"b1b3cc72c46afc09a9d031d33aa4b3b8fdfbdee8","tid":2430080,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd004caea5ef82d978bc5647d3782b3ca43a715c","tid":2430080,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T19:26:43.000Z","msg":"屌....呢D 下九流地方軍頭弱雞到，而家現代人比教學教到帝國主義好撚邪惡，根本呢D 仆街軍頭就需要文明國度既軍隊出兵打撚柒佢，重建秩序。比左半個世紀以上比呢堆低等文化生物自己管自己，結果多年黎都係一篤屎，仲要近埋支那呢個世紀大魔頭度反攻自由世界"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T19:36:43.000Z","msg":"事實證明所謂西方文明自由世界<br />\n都只係顧住自己利益既仆街<br />\n有民主令佢地國內差極有譜<br />\n但你想佢地團結拯救獨裁國家國民？<br />\n咪玩啦，唔撚洗做生意呀？"},{"pid":"936af8cc8ef1b6b84a8990684983b99f729cb222","tid":2430080,"uid":50873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"776a523d931110417e4b75ea36aed4140182a813","tid":2430080,"uid":266342,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T17:44:37.000Z","msg":"新加坡呢班仆街<br />\n到底你隻屎眼睇唔睇到<br />\n其實從頭到尾都係支那作怪<br />\n<br />\n成日話自己個根喺嗰度<br />\n唔好意思福建同廣東係被支那已經一早侵略左<br />\n根本就唔肯認清現實"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T19:54:56.000Z","msg":"人哋就係好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新加坡其中一個重點就係拖死香港，所以只有同香港有關嘅事就必支持PRC。<br />\n<br />\n但去到緬甸呢個case，上面都有人提咗，prc對緬甸影響越大，新加坡地緣政治價值就會削弱。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡先醒啊，prc同美國兩邊跳。係架，好似好無腰骨，但係小國就係要咁跳草裙舞先有so。難聽啲講，你想香港獨立之後經濟好過啲就要學下坡佬嘅手腕。"},{"pid":"ae457818f8a542d5aaf75cdd267af7951e20520b","tid":2430080,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T19:57:13.000Z","msg":"新加坡講嘅嘢好避重就輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好新加坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用民主自決呢啲自己做過嘅字眼<br />\n唔會講啲咩民主自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2d0c147499465f7bff01fa4030c6a007150b0a","tid":2430080,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T20:21:48.000Z","msg":"Monkey國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}